apiVersion: v1
clusters:
- cluster:
    certificate-authority-data: 
    server: https://192.168.56.2:6443
  name: kubernetes
contexts:
- context:
    cluster: kubernetes
    user: kubernetes-admin
  name: kubernetes-admin@kubernetes
current-context: kubernetes-admin@kubernetes
kind: Config
preferences: {}
users:
- name: kubernetes-admin
  user:
    client-certificate-data: 
    client-key-data: 







kubectl config --kubeconfig=kubeadm-cluster.config set clusters.kubernetes.certificate-authority-data 

kubectl config --kubeconfig=kubeadm-cluster.config set-cluster kubernetes --server=https://192.168.56.2

kubectl config --kubeconfig=kubeadm-cluster.config set users.admin.client-certificate-data 

kubectl config --kubeconfig=kubeadm-cluster.config set users.admin.client-key-data
